www.cooperate.market_content_description:
1. Establish partnerships with other watch brands for product promotion and marketing;
2. Cooperate with e-commerce platforms to carry out sales activities of watch products to increase product exposure and sales;
3. Cooperate with fashion media, social media, blogs, etc. to increase brand awareness and exposure;
4. Participate in watch exhibitions, fashion events and other related industry activities to increase brand influence and recognition.

www.cooperate.market_require_description:
1. Have experience in marketing and promotion, understand the watch industry and market;
2. Ability to communicate and negotiate with other brands and e-commerce platforms;
3. Possess good interpersonal skills and be able to establish cooperative relationships with fashion media, social media, blogs, etc.;
4. Possess strong organizational and coordination skills, and be able to organize and participate in relevant industry activities;
5. Possess a certain level of English and be able to conduct cross-border cooperation and communication.
